ZH: 这个国家参加了国际公约。
EN: This country is a signatory to an international convention.

ZH: 桥梁倒塌之后，政府签署了安全公约。
EN: After the bridge collapsed, the government signed a safety convention.

ZH: 这个组织致力于推动环境保护公约的执行。
EN: This organization is dedicated to promoting the implementation of environmental protection conventions.

ZH: 他们通过公约规定了工作人员的权利和义务。
EN: They laid out the rights and obligations of staff through conventions.

ZH: 该公约规定了国家间合作的框架。
EN: The convention sets out the framework for cooperation between countries.

ZH: 这个国家没有签署《气候变化公约》。
EN: This country has not signed the Climate Change Convention.

ZH: 我们需要遵守国际公约的规定。
EN: We need to comply with the provisions of international conventions.

ZH: 共和党和民主党均支持该军控公约。
EN: Both the Republican and Democratic parties support the arms control treaty.

ZH: 该协定规定了两国之间的贸易关系。
EN: The agreement stipulates the trading relationship between the two countries.

ZH: 科学家们呼吁全球领导人签署气候变化公约。
EN: Scientists are calling on global leaders to sign the climate change convention.

ZH: 这项公约旨在促进跨国合作。
EN: This convention aims to promote international cooperation.

ZH: 全球反恐公约被视为保护和平的重要法律工具。
EN: The global anti-terrorism convention is seen as an important legal tool for promoting peace.

ZH: 国际组织制定了一套反歧视公约。
EN: International organizations have developed a set of anti-discrimination conventions.

ZH: 由于未能遵守公约，该国将面临国际制裁。
EN: Failure to comply with the convention will result in international sanctions against the country.

ZH: 各国领导人将就签署公约进行协商。
EN: Leaders of various countries will negotiate the signing of the convention.

ZH: 这份公约旨在保护儿童权益。
EN: This convention aims to protect the rights of children

ZH: 人权公约规定了每个人的基本权利。
EN: The Human Rights Convention sets out the fundamental rights of every person.

ZH: 已经有超过100个国家签署了该协定。
EN: Over 100 countries have already signed the agreement.

ZH: 签署《核裁军公约》是一场关键的峰会议题。
EN: Signing the Nuclear Disarmament Convention is a key agenda item at the summit.

ZH: 该国政府承诺履行气候变化公约。
EN: The government of this country has committed to fulfilling the Climate Change Convention.
